<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chung Pathien sam suihin tuona pi leh pute,
 A kigawm ui sietlei luoh ding, vawnchawi di'n;
 Chung Pathien lai tanna thimthu gui bang zawtin
 Sietlei chungah vawn zatam chibang a hun theh ui

[V2]
 Aw Lalpa, ka ngetnau ngaiin
 Zie thutiem hi Nang hun zawmin
 Tu-a lungsietna gui khau bang zawp hi
 Chin leh tuoi leh guol lungtuok ten
 Chung Pathien leh lei mite angah
 Ka hetpih chiet ui

[V3]
 2. Lalpa, Na dan thienga chawnban hun zawmte hin
 Zuomang min siel thimthu duh ai bang samin
 Damlai kawlni a liem man pallai lo bang chul leh
 Thimthu tiemah kumsawt in kigawm det uh hen

[V4]
 3. Tuon leh tanga pi pu lung mawlte dungsun in,
 Pai tin chawia ki lungsietna tawplo di'n
 Chung Pathien samsuih thutiem lam bang pel loin
 Phunglai chawi thiem pai kuoh di'n Aw Lalpa vang hun pie'n.</lyrics>
<title>Chung Pathien Samsuih</title>
<author>Sawngkhawkhai</author>
<hymn_number>257</hymn_number>
</song>